data.name: Instructions.Text
data.value: Download and locate the hie and seek base folder. Create PC_External in the same folder as your Ty.exe and locate. Go to where you want an opal, press the Get Current Ty Pos button and copy the values into the boxes.

data.name: DLLPatchWarning.Text
data.value: Ty could crash if the DLL is left unpatched. Select the folder containing Ty.exe and press patchDLL. You are not allowed (or able) to speedrun Ty with the patched DLL. If you plan on running, select the folder and press unpatchDLL.
